document_data.Inhabitants:
Nothing of worth was left in Maskana, but a few [[Uropygus|giant whip scorpions]] may have hunted there from time to time.

The hidden sublevel was protected by [[helmed horror]]s, [[crawling claw]]s, and a trapped room where the walls would come together to crush anyone inside.<ref>{{Cite web enhancement/Secrets of Imaskar|7}}

Tyaral, a priest of Bhaal, may have had two [[flameskull]]s with himself for protection.
